msgctxt "Description|"
msgid ""
"This module offers a Bayesian take on linear Gaussian state space models "
"suitable for   time series analysis."
msgstr ""
"Modul ini menawarkan model spasi status pengambilan Bayes pada Gaussian "
"linear dapat disesuaikan untuk   analisis seri waktu."

